column5: Got out with a friend to my first ice fishing trip of the season! Marked a lot of fish but we only managed one but it was a good one!! Just hammered my williams! sparky
Nice fish! How is your ice over that way this year?
That is a dandy laker, thanks for sharing!
Nice fish! Man I wish we had those around hereâ€¦
On Simcoe there is a good foot and a half to two feet of ice on the entire lake now but there is also a lot of snow too. sparky
